CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Akoya Biosciences Inc is an innovative life sciences technology company. It is delivering spatial biology solutions focused on transforming discovery and clinical research. The company offers the most comprehensive, end-to-end solutions for high-parameter tissue analysis from discovery through clinical and translational research, enabling the development of more precise therapies for immuno-oncology and other drug development applications.
